name: Sword
long_description: A rusty sword. Doesn't really fit in your bag.

name: Potion
long_description: A red potion that has "POTION" written across it. (+40 health)

name: Damage-Up
long_description: An orange potion that has "DAMAGE UP" written across it. (x1.2 damage)

name: Trident
long_description: A sharp three pronged weapon. You could make like, at least two roasted marshmallows.

name: Gold Key
long_description: A super shiny key! Probably unlocks a door, but what do I know.

name: Shuttle Pass
long_description: A blue pass to ride the shuttle. The road awaits!

name: Paint Brush
long_description: Paint your enemies??

name: Dagger
long_description: A trusty dagger that fits in your back pocket.

name: Gauntlets
long_description: Reliable Gauntlets will help you attack harder.

name: Armor
long_description: Weak armor will increase your health.

name: Helmet
long_description: Weak armor will increase your health.

name: Pants
long_description: Weak armor will increase your health.

name: Stick
long_description: A sturdy wooden stick. Useful for crafting.

name: String
long_description: A length of string. Useful for crafting.

name: Pencil
long_description: A sharp pencil, useful for writing... or stabbing.

name: Spork of Doom
long_description: Forged in the fires of the dining hall dishwasher. Useful for soup or steak.

name: Textbook
long_description: The title is UML Distilled". I have never read it."

name: 3D Printer Arm
long_description: A repurposed printer arm with servo strength. Prints pain in real time.

name: Wire Lasso
long_description: Strands of live wire braided together. Shocking and stylish.

name: Capstone Cannon
long_description: Your final project turned into a portable, shoulder-mounted problem solver.

name: Orb of Vengeance
long_description: It's red, rubber, and full of trauma. Hits harder than your GPA drop after midterms.

name: Spork Supreme
long_description: Forged from rare alloys and blessed by the Lunch Lady. The final form of all utensils.

name: A reference to a sword
long_description: It is said this sword is the only weapon that can help you pass CS320. It answers any question the BABHAKE throws at you!

name: Coffee Mug Smash
long_description: A cracked ceramic mug from the campus caf√©. Delivers scalding justice.

name: Textbook Club
long_description: Thick, overpriced, and finally useful for something.

name: Fire Alarm Bludgeon
long_description: Ripped straight off the wall. Not campus-approved.

name: Dining Tray Shieldbash
long_description: Once used for pizza. Now for punishment.

name: Broom Handle Spear
long_description: From janitor closet to javelin. Surprisingly stabby.

name: Laptop Charger Flail
long_description: The weight of a brick and the rage of a dead battery.

name: Water Bottle Launcher
long_description: Spring-loaded hydration assault. Hits like a plastic meteor.

name: Chair Leg Mace
long_description: Broken in a dorm brawl. Reforged for battle.

name: Whiteboard Javelin
long_description: It squeaks. It shatters. It skewers dreams.

name: Tripod Blaster
long_description: For every hour it took to set up, it repays in pain.

name: Projector Core
long_description: Ripped from the ceiling. Still hot. Still deadly.

name: Recycling Bin Slammer
long_description: Overflowing with rage and discarded essays.

name: Metal Railing Pipe
long_description: Campus infrastructure repurposed into wrath incarnate.

name: Stolen Scooter Ram
long_description: Ride it straight into chaos. Campus police disapprove.

name: Fire Extinguisher Blast
long_description: Pull the pin, unleash frosty doom. Also puts out study fires.

name: Cold Pizza Slice
long_description: A questionable slice from three nights ago. Still good.

name: Cafeteria Mystery Meat
long_description: No one knows what it is. Somehow, it helps.

name: Energy Bar
long_description: Dry, dense, and exactly what your body needs. Kind of.

name: Instant Ramen
long_description: High sodium. Higher morale.

name: Cheesy Nachos
long_description: Crispy, gooey, and emotionally supportive.

name: Bag of Trail Mix
long_description: Mostly raisins. But healing raisins.

name: Microwave Burrito
long_description: Explosive flavor. Possibly explosive in other ways.

name: Campus Smoothie
long_description: It's green. It's weird. It works.

name: Leftover Fries
long_description: Soggy but full of memories... and carbs.

name: Finals Week Donut
long_description: Covered in frosting and desperation. A sugary morale boost.

long_description: " Pair of Author Books"

long_description: "Monty Python's Holy Grail! Try to SQL Query that!"

long_description: "Used to craft a strong weapon"
